paragraphs.title: Fichiers csv (display - html)
paragraphs.text:
%sh echo "%html" echo '' echo "" for csv in $(ls /data/*csv) do csv_size=$(stat -c%s "$csv") echo "" done echo "
Fichiers disponiblesTaille
$csv$csv_size
"

paragraphs.title: Fichiers csv (display - table)
paragraphs.text:
%sh

echo "%table"
echo -e "Fichiers disponibles\tTaille"
for csv in $(ls /data/*csv)
do
  csv_size=$(stat -c%s "$csv")
  echo -e "$csv\t$csv_size"
done

paragraphs.title: Init de la table 'bank' (Spark)
paragraphs.text:
%spark

case class Bank(age:Integer, job:String, marital : String, education : String, balance : Integer)

val bankText = sc.textFile("/data/bank.csv")

val bank = bankText.map(s=>s.split(";")).filter(s=>s(0)!="\"age\"").map(
    s=>Bank(s(0).toInt, 
            s(1).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(3).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(5).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt
        )
)

bank.toDF().registerTempTable("bank")

defined class Bank

paragraphs.title: Répartition par âge
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select age, count(1) as count from bank 
where age < ${AgeMax=30} and job = "${Job=unemployed,management|self-employed|services|technician|unemployed}"
group by age order by age
